      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POPPY'S DARLIN' (7) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (23.48) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including five wins. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Has ability and looks hard to stop. MR. SPECKLE (3) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (23.29) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has a good record here including two wins. Great chance to atone. US AND THEM (1) produced a modest effort most recently when eighth at Gosford over 388m behind My Wee Lass (23.09) in a Grade 5. Can measure up this time. CHUTZPAH (2) will give backers a sight.",
